    • Method Detail

      • process

        Collection<? extends Artifact> process(MavenProject project,
                                       Collection<? extends Artifact> artifacts,
                                       Log log)
                                throws ArtifactsProcessingException
        Performs some operation on the supplied Collection of Artifacts in the context of the supplied MavenProject and returns a Collection of Artifacts representing the result.

        Implementations of this method are permitted to return null.

        Implementations of this method are permitted to return the supplied Collection of Artifacts.

        Implementations of this method are permitted to mutate the supplied Collection and/or any of its elements.

        Implementations of this method must not mutate the supplied MavenProject.

        Parameters:
        project - the MavenProject in the context of which processing will take place; must not be null
        artifacts - the Artifacts to process; may be null
        log - the Log to use when logging; may be null
        Returns:
        a Collection of Artifacts representing the result of processing, or null
        Throws:
        ArtifactsProcessingException - if an error occurs
        See Also:
        ArtifactMojo, Artifact, MavenProject
